{"tid":58800,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"同呀妹嗌交嗌到把幾火，一巴打到佢入廠","createTime":"2016-12-29T06:34:11.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-29T09:42:06.000Z","uid":5190,"like":78,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4a76af09e4835bc1467d8c4dcf6d8b00e962b2a0","tid":58800,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T06:34:11.000Z","msg":"事源呀妹同老豆老母講野嘅時候比我偷聽到佢話要去朋友屋企過夜 有男有女 老豆老母都叫佢唔好去 你16歲卜卜脆容乜易比人屌 但呀妹嘅mk性格 邊有咁易投降 佢係咁話無事嘅無事嘅 喂 大佬 係人都知成班人夜晚晚係屋企仲要係mk仔女會搞咩啦 佢仲岸鳩鳩咁 一陣豬都比人食埋<br />\n<br />\n我睇唔過眼 決定用呀哥嘅身份去屌醒佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 妹<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好心你啦 呀爸呀媽都係擔心你姐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我咁大個人有分數啦！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你幾大呀？成年未呀？咁大口氣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 16歲啦 仲要你管<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就係16歲先要更小心呀<br />\n<br />\n去到依個位開始愈黎愈大聲 氣氛愈黎愈高漲 我同佢都愈黎愈嬲 但我地都盡量避免講扑野依個話題 廢事老豆老母擔心 直到...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 16歲扑得野添啦 其他野仲洗你理？<br />\n<br />\n係依個時候 dead air 左幾秒 我為左打破個dead air 我決定一巴打落呀妹到 再加多句...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 死女包！！<br />\n<br />\n可能我大力得濟 一巴打撚到佢瞓左落地 原本都無乜野 見佢神智仲清醒 但見到佢隻手好似好痛咁 原來佢跌落地個陣 手爭一野挫左落地下塊地板上面 仲挫到裂撚埋 我先知依鋪搞大左 佢喊晒口 我都唔知點補救 老母緊第一時間打電話call白車 老豆就去睇下呀妹隻手點 <br />\n<br />\n我哀坐係到 望住塊地板 唔知點算 老豆老母實好撚憎我 佢地同呀妹去醫院 叫我今晚自己搞掂佢 我好似比人拋棄左咁 我真係唔知點搞好 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想問下巴絲有無地板公司介紹下 整返好塊地板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2236a4599b0200887f3797793a8c979309c06d73","tid":58800,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T06:35:50.000Z","msg":"家暴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c4f582b2ffc38a0e0ab90dbfd90f3f7c779ce83","tid":58800,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T06:36:01.000Z","msg":"仲以為係你個妹裂左"},{"pid":"ba449175bd2b5f35301ee75b27e45a248dffc8b7","tid":58800,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T06:38:12.000Z","msg":"Ching ho ball ar"},{"pid":"1a11dfeb797c8b19a5b0e261fd8b926e38f62ca3","tid":58800,"uid":16685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T06:38:15.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"e3bee001076781657c52f900dffb5a4e4cbc82af","tid":58800,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T06:38:19.000Z","msg":"未睇諗住覆我識人整on<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87949f892fe2d4649e2fe2c3fb418f20c5c0bf55","tid":58800,"uid":40737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T06:38:34.000Z","msg":"整返好部iphone 先"},{"pid":"da1a2598c5744c403307670dbd96c9fd4a7479ad","tid":58800,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T06:38:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未睇諗住覆我識人整<span style=\"color: red;\">mon</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"edb7dc94a67304f55e8293490b5dd05ee3f08a5f","tid":58800,"uid":12475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T06:39:11.000Z","msg":"以為有甜<br />\n負皮上一頁"},{"pid":"1159c6954b0705e61f58c4e2c9adc61b98337918","tid":58800,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T06:39:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以為有甜<br />\n負皮上一頁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打到入廠仲點甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a03dafe33b73d6eafbdf68d9ae85fe0241f8ace","tid":58800,"uid":12475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T06:39:49.000Z","msg":"BTW 睇錯一巴打屌到佢入廠"},{"pid":"326be283f91cb324942fec2cafc6827